title: 04/14/2021 - Hour 3 - Can't Believe in the Cowboys
itunes:title: 04/14/2021 - Hour 3 - Can't Believe in the Cowboys
description:
LaVar Arrington, TJ Houshmandzadeh and Plaxico Burress are filling in for Dan Patrick and the Danettes, debating whether or not the Cowboys' window for winning a Super Bowl has closed. They discuss the new rules surrounding COVID vaccinations in the NFL and whether Zion Williamson will be the new face of the NBA.
